        "payload": "tree fbd36019dec95c9b9c8942a9b5786b2e79e265d8\nparent 2cfb10b668f628596e38506c0b0243840a906ff1\nauthor Andrew Toth <andrewstoth@gmail.com> 1781475314 -0400\ncommitter Andrew Toth <andrewstoth@gmail.com> 1781475314 -0400\n\ntxindex: use siphash keys to optimize disk usage\n\nUse an 8-byte salted siphash to key txindex entries,\ninstead of the full 32-byte txid. Store the tx position\nafter the hash in the key, so an iterator can scan\nthrough any collisions and return the correct tx.\n\nFallback to the legacy key lookup if the tx is not found.\n",
